2. REVERSE ARRAY

---

class ReverseArray {
public static void main(String[] args) {
int[] arr = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5};

```
    int left = 0, right = arr.length - 1;

    while (left < right) {
        int temp = arr[left];
        arr[left] = arr[right];
        arr[right] = temp;

        left++;
        right--;
    }

    for (int num : arr) {
        System.out.print(num + " ");
    }
}
```

}

