4. MOVE ZEROES

---

class MoveZeroes {
public static void main(String[] args) {
int[] arr = {0, 1, 0, 3, 12};

```
    int index = 0;

    for (int i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
        if (arr[i] != 0) {
            arr[index++] = arr[i];
        }
    }

    while (index < arr.length) {
        arr[index++] = 0;
    }

    for (int num : arr) {
        System.out.print(num + " ");
    }
}
```

}

