6. REMOVE DUPLICATES (SORTED)

---

class RemoveDuplicates {
public static void main(String[] args) {
int[] arr = {1, 1, 2, 2, 3, 4, 4};

```
    int index = 1;

    for (int i = 1; i < arr.length; i++) {
        if (arr[i] != arr[i - 1]) {
            arr[index++] = arr[i];
        }
    }

    for (int i = 0; i < index; i++) {
        System.out.print(arr[i] + " ");
    }
}
```

}

