10. FIND MISSING NUMBER

---

class MissingNumber {
public static void main(String[] args) {
int[] arr = {3, 0, 1};

```
    int n = arr.length;
    int total = n * (n + 1) / 2;

    int sum = 0;
    for (int num : arr) {
        sum += num;
    }

    System.out.println("Missing: " + (total - sum));
}
```

}

